{"snp2.12:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.12 ","snp2.12:0.2":"Nigrodhakappa (vangisa) sutta ","snp2.12:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp2.12:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava alaviyam viharati aggalave cetiye. ","snp2.12:1.3":"Tena kho pana samayena ayasmato vangisassa upajjhayo nigrodhakappo nama thero aggalave cetiye aciraparinibbuto hoti. ","snp2.12:1.4":"Atha kho ayasmato vangisassa rahogatassa patisallinassa evam cetaso parivitakko udapadi—","snp2.12:1.5":"parinibbuto nu kho me upajjhayo udahu no parinibbutoti? ","snp2.12:1.6":"Atha kho ayasma vangiso sayanhasamayam patisallana vutthito yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam nisidi. Ekamantam nisinno kho ayasma vangiso bhagavantam etadavoca—","snp2.12:1.7":"idha mayham, bhante, rahogatassa patisallinassa evam cetaso parivitakko udapadi—","snp2.12:1.8":"parinibbuto nu kho me upajjhayo, udahu no parinibbutoti. ","snp2.12:1.9":"Atha kho ayasma vangiso utthayasana ekamsam civaram katva yena bhagava tenanjalim panametva bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","snp2.12:2.1":"“Pucchami sattharamanomapannam, ","snp2.12:2.2":"Dittheva dhamme yo vicikicchanam chetta; ","snp2.12:2.3":"Aggalave kalamakasi bhikkhu, ","snp2.12:2.4":"Nato yasassi abhinibbutatto. ","snp2.12:3.1":"Nigrodhakappo iti tassa namam, ","snp2.12:3.2":"Taya katam bhagava brahmanassa; ","snp2.12:3.3":"So tam namassam acari mutyapekkho, ","snp2.12:3.4":"Araddhaviriyo dalhadhammadassi. ","snp2.12:4.1":"Tam savakam sakya mayampi sabbe, ","snp2.12:4.2":"Annatumicchama samantacakkhu; ","snp2.12:4.3":"Samavatthita no savanaya sota, ","snp2.12:4.4":"Tuvam no sattha tvamanuttarosi. ","snp2.12:5.1":"Chindeva no vicikiccham bruhi metam, ","snp2.12:5.2":"Parinibbutam vedaya bhuripanna; ","snp2.12:5.3":"Majjheva no bhasa samantacakkhu, ","snp2.12:5.4":"Sakkova devana sahassanetto. ","snp2.12:6.1":"Ye keci gantha idha mohamagga, ","snp2.12:6.2":"Annanapakkha vicikicchathana; ","snp2.12:6.3":"Tathagatam patva na te bhavanti, ","snp2.12:6.4":"Cakkhunhi etam paramam naranam. ","snp2.12:7.1":"No ce hi jatu puriso kilese, ","snp2.12:7.2":"Vato yatha abbhaghanam vihane; ","snp2.12:7.3":"Tamovassa nivuto sabbaloko, ","snp2.12:7.4":"Na jotimantopi nara tapeyyum. ","snp2.12:8.1":"Dhira ca pajjotakara bhavanti, ","snp2.12:8.2":"Tam tam aham vira tatheva manne; ","snp2.12:8.3":"Vipassinam janamupagamumha, ","snp2.12:8.4":"Parisasu no avikarohi kappam. ","snp2.12:9.1":"Khippam giram eraya vaggu vaggum, ","snp2.12:9.2":"Hamsova paggayha sanikam nikuja; ","snp2.12:9.3":"Bindussarena suvikappitena, ","snp2.12:9.4":"Sabbeva te ujjugata sunoma. ","snp2.12:10.1":"Pahinajatimaranam asesam, ","snp2.12:10.2":"Niggayha dhonam vadessami dhammam; ","snp2.12:10.3":"Na kamakaro hi puthujjananam, ","snp2.12:10.4":"Sankheyyakaro ca tathagatanam. ","snp2.12:11.1":"Sampannaveyyakaranam tavedam, ","snp2.12:11.2":"Samujjupannassa samuggahitam; ","snp2.12:11.3":"Ayamanjali pacchimo suppanamito, ","snp2.12:11.4":"Ma mohayi janamanomapanna. ","snp2.12:12.1":"Parovaram ariyadhammam viditva, ","snp2.12:12.2":"Ma mohayi janamanomavira; ","snp2.12:12.3":"Varim yatha ghammani ghammatatto, ","snp2.12:12.4":"Vacabhikankhami sutam pavassa. ","snp2.12:13.1":"Yadatthikam brahmacariyam acari, ","snp2.12:13.2":"Kappayano kaccissa tam amogham; ","snp2.12:13.3":"Nibbayi so adu saupadiseso, ","snp2.12:13.4":"Yatha vimutto ahu tam sunoma”. ","snp2.12:14.1":"“Acchecchi tanham idha namarupe, ","snp2.12:14.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp2.12:14.3":"Kanhassa sotam digharattanusayitam; ","snp2.12:14.4":"Atari jatim maranam asesam”, ","snp2.12:14.5":"Iccabravi bhagava pancasettho. ","snp2.12:15.1":"“Esa sutva pasidami, ","snp2.12:15.2":"Vaco te isisattama; ","snp2.12:15.3":"Amogham kira me puttham, ","snp2.12:15.4":"Na mam vancesi brahmano. ","snp2.12:16.1":"Yathavadi tathakari, ","snp2.12:16.2":"Ahu buddhassa savako; ","snp2.12:16.3":"Acchida maccuno jalam, ","snp2.12:16.4":"Tatam mayavino dalham. ","snp2.12:17.1":"Addasa bhagava adim, ","snp2.12:17.2":"Upadanassa kappiyo; ","snp2.12:17.3":"Accaga vata kappayano, ","snp2.12:17.4":"Maccudheyyam suduttaran”ti. ","snp2.12:17.5":"Nigrodhakappasuttam dvadasamam. "}